cs.IR, cs.DL, cs.CY, cs.CR, cs.DB

This paper deals with the aggregation and analysis of usage data in scholarly information services, which is closely related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and digital libraries (cs.DL). It also involves issues related to cybersecurity (cs.CY) and cryptography (cs.CR) due to concerns regarding user privacy. Additionally, the paper discusses the implementation of a technical architecture, which involves database systems (cs.DB).
